    <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://ies.data.gov.uk/ontology/ies4#State> .

<http://example.org/ontology/ies-building#ClassOfCondensingBoiler> a <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#Class> ;
